role, and I believe Flowers does as well. MA Armor doesn't fill the chemical protection I want and I also don't like how high sense needs to be for you to wear it. The requirements on equal STR/AGI armor is much easier to obtain for me. Like I said, I'm a Solitus..not an Opifex. <br><br>That's my personal opinion on what I'm going to be looking for. Don't follow this as rote, because I could be completely off base with it. I'm not a genious. I do, once again, suggest deciding on an armor schema now so that you can buy it at a cheaper price before the armor gets buffed with 12.5. Plus, if you stick to your guns on the type of armor you want, and not buying on impulse, you'll end up with a better set of armor and a larger pool of credits. <br><br>Just a friendly note from yer uncle Yaoshi.<br> <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub83.ezboard.com/ufhastal.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Fhastal</A> at: 8/14/01 11:59:46 am<br></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub83.ezboard.com/fthepunchingbag74708frm2.showPrevMessage?topicID=121.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub83.ezboard.com/fthepunchingbag74708frm2.showNextMessage?topicID=121.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub83.ezboard.com/fthepunchingbag74708frm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=121.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/far_east/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub83.ezboard.com/fthepunchingbag74708frm2.emailToFriend?topicID=121.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub83.ezboard.com/fthepunchingbag74708frm2.threadControl?topicID=121.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/far_east/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image